This paper is primarily focused on object detection using computer vision techniques, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also utilizes deep learning algorithms, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of state-of-the-art algorithms and techniques for object detection also suggests that the paper may fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of robotics for object detection, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper involves the use of image and video processing techniques, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
